                            <comment id="12977602" author="daijy" created="Wed, 5 Jan 2011 03:02:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Mostly in PigServer. It consists of these tasks:&lt;br/&gt;
1. Move describe/nested describe to new logical plan&lt;br/&gt;
2. Move Graph to new logical plan&lt;br/&gt;
3. Move scalar merge to new logical plan&lt;br/&gt;
4. Move UnionOnSchemaSetter to new logical plan&lt;br/&gt;
5. Remove SortInfoSetter (since it&apos;s already in new logical plan)&lt;br/&gt;
6. Other cleanup in PigServer&lt;br/&gt;
7. Test cases&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
